  "instructions": [
    "In a wok or large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the finely chopped garlic and sauté for about 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Next, add the finely chopped beets, leeks, red bell pepper, watermelon radish, and bay leaves. Stir fry everything together until they are heated through and the vegetables have softened slightly.",
